00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,260
Something did happen to her.

431
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:31,700
She's gone.

432
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:32,820
It's pretty tragic.

433
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:34,060
If you know anything,

434
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:35,380
