00:23:40,060 --> 00:23:41,060
No, I don't.

466
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,110
We're collecting some of

467
00:23:43,110 --> 00:23:44,980
Ai Lin's personal items as evidence.

468
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:46,060
But the janitor said

469
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,210
everything was thrown out.

470
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:49,100
I don't have any.

471
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:50,380
We weren't

472
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:51,580
that close.

473
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:58,620
Alright.

474
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:41,420
Do you know

475
00:24:41,420 --> 00:24:42,420
