533
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:25,700
Tell me.

534
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:27,940
Did the girl have any close friends?

535
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:29,140
Especially male?

536
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,060
No.

537
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:32,260
